<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Welcome to Carbon Footprint Tracker</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .feature {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Carbon Footprint Tracker!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Welcome to Carbon Footprint Tracker! We're excited to have you join our community of environmentally conscious individuals.</p>

        <h2>What You Can Do</h2>
        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Track Your Carbon Footprint</h3>
            <p>Use our calculator to track your daily activities and their environmental impact.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Join Challenges</h3>
            <p>Participate in community challenges to reduce your carbon footprint and earn achievements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature">
            <h3>Get Weekly Reports</h3>
            <p>Receive detailed weekly reports about your progress and tips to improve.</p>
        </div>

        <p>Ready to start your sustainability journey?</p>
        <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 